{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b8f4a9c1-tontine-x360-e2e",
    "name": "TontineX360 — API E2E",
    "description": "# TontineX360 — Collection Postman complète\n\nTeste l'ensemble du flux applicatif : auth → onboarding → configuration tontine → runtime (séances, cotisations, enchères, distributions) → wallet & clôture.\n\n## Variables d'environnement à définir\n\n| Variable | Description | Exemple |\n|---|---|---|\n| `base_url` | URL du backend | `https://tontine-project.onrender.com` |\n| `tenant_slug` | Slug de l'asso active (auto-set après login) | `e-drtim` |\n| `access_token` | JWT access (auto-set après login) | ... |\n| `refresh_token` | JWT refresh (auto-set après login) | ... |\n| `user_phone` | Téléphone du user pour les tests | `+237655362943` |\n| `user_password` | Password du user pour les tests | `SuperSecret123!` |\n\n## Ordre recommandé pour un test E2E\n\n1. **Auth** : Register → Login (les tokens sont sauvegardés automatiquement)\n2. **Associations** : Créer / Rejoindre / Sélectionner\n3. **Members** : Inviter des membres, gérer les demandes\n4. **Tontines** : Créer un type + un cycle\n5. **Cycle** : Souscription + Ouvrir un pot\n6. **Runtime** : Cotiser → Séances → Enchères → Distributions\n7. **Wallet** : Consulter son wallet + entries\n8. **Clôture** : Fermer pot, fermer cycle, settlement\n\n## Header X-Tenant\n\nToutes les requêtes multi-tenant utilisent `X-Tenant: {{tenant_slug}}` — auto-injecté après avoir sélectionné une asso.\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Injecte X-Tenant automatiquement si tenant_slug est défini",
          "const slug = pm.variables.get('tenant_slug');",
          "if (slug && !pm.request.headers.has('X-Tenant')) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'X-Tenant', value: slug });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://tontine-project.onrender.com" },
    { "key": "tenant_slug", "value": "" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "user_phone", "value": "+237655362943" },
    { "key": "user_password", "value": "ChangeMe123!" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Authentication",
      "description": "Register, login, refresh, forgot password.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (nouveau user)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register", ""] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"telephone\": \"{{user_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Steve\",\n  \"last_name\": \"Kameni\",\n  \"email\": \"steve.test@example.com\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (récupère JWT)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.tokens?.access) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', j.tokens.access);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', j.tokens.refresh);",
                  "  console.log('Tokens sauvegardés.');",
                  "}",
                  "if (j.user?.id) console.log('User: ' + j.user.telephone);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login", ""] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"telephone\": \"{{user_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.access) pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', j.access);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/token/refresh/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "token", "refresh", ""] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (profil courant)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "me", ""] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change password (authentifié)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/change-password/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "change-password", ""] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"old_password\": \"{{user_password}}\",\n  \"new_password\": \"NewSecret456!\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password — Request OTP",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/change-fogot-password/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "change-fogot-password", ""] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"telephone\": \"{{user_phone}}\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password — Verify OTP + Reset",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/valid-otp/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "valid-otp", ""] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"telephone\": \"{{user_phone}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\",\n  \"new_password\": \"NewSecret456!\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "FCM — Enregistrer un token push",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register-fcm-token/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register-fcm-token", ""] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"dQwxxxxxxxxxxxxx_TOKEN_FCM_ICI\",\n  \"device_type\": \"web\"\n}" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
